    "a": "P(X=k) = \\frac{e^{-\\lambda} \\lambda^k}{k!}"
  },
  {
    "q": "Esperanza y Varianza Poisson",
    "a": "E[X] = \\lambda; Var(X) = \\lambda"
  },
  {
